			Company Description 


			Sundance Strategies, Inc. is an innovative company, which provides insurance brokerage services. It engages in structuring related insurance contracts, policies and obligations into secure, reinsured Net Insurance Benefits. The company includes notes, drafts, acceptances, open accounts receivable, o...
		


                Sundance Strategies, Inc. is an innovative company, which provides insurance brokerage services. It engages in structuring related insurance contracts, policies and obligations into secure, reinsured Net Insurance Benefits. The company includes notes, drafts, acceptances, open accounts receivable, other obligations representing part or all of the sales price of insurance, life settlements and, related insurance contracts. Sundance Strategies was founded on December 14, 2001 and is headquartered in Provo, UT.
            




