	we recorded net cash used in operating activities of $124,205, compared to $1,818,262 used in operating activities during the nine
	months ended December 31, 2015. The increase in operating cash flows was primarily due to the receipt of approximately $1,400,000,
	which was an approved distribution from the policy owners as a return on our interest in NIBs.


	 


